<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Privacy Policy | Meno - Daily Planner</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for Meno - Daily Planner.">
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: dark;
      --bg: #07111f;
      --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --card-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      --text: #f8fafc;
      --muted: #b7c4d4;
      --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      --primary: #38bdf8;
      --accent: #22d3ee;
      --success: #22c55e;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.65;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.23), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 14%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.16), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #06101f 0%, #0a1628 54%, #07111f 100%);
    }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .page { width: min(1040px, calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; padding: 56px 0; }
    .hero {
      padding: 44px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05));
      box-shadow: 0 28px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.36);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #d8f3ff;
      background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--success); box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9); }
    h1 { margin: 24px 0 12px; font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 6vw, 4.5rem); line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -0.04em; }
    .subtitle { max-width: 760px; margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: clamp(1.02rem, 2vw, 1.2rem); }
    .updated { margin-top: 22px; color: #d7e6f4; font-weight: 700; }
    .content { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr; gap: 28px; margin-top: 28px; align-items: start; }
    nav { position: sticky; top: 20px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 22px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06); backdrop-filter: blur(14px); }
    nav strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    nav a { display: block; padding: 8px 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.94rem; }
    main { display: grid; gap: 18px; }
    section { padding: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 22px; background: var(--card); backdrop-filter: blur(14px); }
    h2 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 1.28rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    p { margin: 0 0 12px; color: var(--muted); }
    p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    ul { margin: 12px 0 0; padding-left: 22px; color: var(--muted); }
    li { margin: 8px 0; }
    .callout { border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.34); background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.13), rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.07)); }
    footer { margin-top: 28px; padding: 24px; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; }
    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .page { width: min(100% - 22px, 1040px); padding: 28px 0; }
      .hero, section { padding: 24px; border-radius: 20px; }
      .content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      nav { position: static; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header class="hero">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> Privacy Policy</span>
      <h1>Meno - Daily Planner</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Meno helps you plan your day, build habits, write diary entries, manage your calendar, and receive reminders while keeping your data local-first.</p>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: June 17, 2026</p>
    </header>
    <div class="content">
      <nav aria-label="Privacy policy sections">
        <strong>Contents</strong>
        <a href="#overview">Overview</a>
        <a href="#data">Information We Handle</a>
        <a href="#local">Local Device Storage</a>
        <a href="#notifications">Notifications</a>
        <a href="#ads">AdMob Advertising</a>
        <a href="#selling">No Sale of Personal Information</a>
        <a href="#deletion">Data Deletion</a>
        <a href="#children">Children's Privacy</a>
        <a href="#changes">Changes</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <main>
        <section id="overview" class="callout">
          <h2>Overview</h2>
          <p>This Privacy Policy explains how Meno - Daily Planner ("Meno", "we", "our", or "the app") handles information. Meno is designed as a productivity app with local-first storage.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="data">
          <h2>Information We Handle</h2>
          <p>Meno may help you create and manage:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Tasks, projects, due dates, priorities, labels, and completion status.</li>
            <li>Habits, habit targets, progress, streaks, and reminder preferences.</li>
            <li>Diary or journal entries, moods, labels, and personal reflections.</li>
            <li>Calendar events, planning information, dates, and reminders.</li>
            <li>App settings such as language, theme, notification preferences, and profile display name.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="local">
          <h2>Local Device Storage</h2>
          <p>User data is primarily stored locally on the user's device. Meno does not require an account for core use and does not sell or operate a cloud database for your personal productivity content by default.</p>
          <p>If you export or back up your data, that exported file is controlled by you. Anyone with access to that file may be able to read the information inside it.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="notifications">
          <h2>Notifications</h2>
          <p>Meno uses notifications for reminders, including tasks, habits, diary reflection, calendar events, daily motivation, streak protection, and weekly review. Notifications are optional and can be controlled in the app and in your device settings.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="ads">
          <h2>AdMob Advertising</h2>
          <p>Meno may show advertisements using Google AdMob. AdMob may collect advertising identifiers, analytics data, device information, app interaction data, and related information according to Google's policies.</p>
          <p>Learn more about Google's advertising practices at <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Policies - Advertising</a>.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="selling">
          <h2>No Sale of Personal Information</h2>
          <p>Meno does not sell personal information. Your personal productivity content remains primarily on your device unless you choose to export, share, or send it.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="deletion">
          <h2>Data Deletion</h2>
          <p>You can delete local data by deleting items inside Meno, clearing app data, deleting backups you created, or uninstalling the app. You can also request data deletion help by contacting the developer by email.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="children">
          <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Meno is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has contacted us or shared personal information, please email us.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="changes">
          <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy as Meno evolves. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised date.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="contact" class="callout">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy questions or data deletion requests, contact the developer at <a href="mailto:shadysaberalmelden@gmail.com">shadysaberalmelden@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
    <footer>Meno - Daily Planner. Plan. Build. Grow.</footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
